{"tid":2489710,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭評分再下跌 逾四成人予零分 3司評分全部肥佬","createTime":"2021-04-15T06:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T06:46:49.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f3f8c4d4d3995230b69cbc80f68add536d94d0b6","tid":2489710,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:13:20.000Z","msg":"北京閹割香港選舉制度，民間呈現出「心死」狀態。有民調顯示，對比人大常委會上月底通過「完善」選制前，市民對特首林鄭月娥的評分下跌2.1分，至30.7分水平，而支持林鄭的比率則略為上升。<br />\n<br />\n市民對林鄭反對率微跌1個百分點至67%<br />\n香港民意研究計劃於本月7至9日成功訪問了逾千名市民。結果顯示，市民對林鄭的評分，由上月下旬的32.8分跌至30.7分，而支持率更則微升兩個百分點至20%、反對率微跌1個百分點至67%，使支持率淨值增加3個百分點至負47%。惟細分之下，給予林鄭0分的市民多達41%。<br />\n<br />\n3名司長方面，市民對政務司司長張建宗和律政司司長鄭若驊的評分都有所下調，分別下跌0.1分及1.2分至32.6分及22.7分。至於市民對財政司司長陳茂波的評分，則稍稍增加了1.1分，達35.8分水平。換言之，無論林鄭或3名司長的民望均處於不及格水平。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i83iCbwILR5cAdA6ydmo7FjklgY=/802x891/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WRNL2E3JLVGKLJIBOUGQU7EN34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi83iCbwILR5cAdA6ydmo7FjklgY%3D%2F802x891%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWRNL2E3JLVGKLJIBOUGQU7EN34.jpg&h=8ea93435&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"808578ac7db1d8fb8b3e00540380eb2904512e23","tid":2489710,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:21:15.000Z","msg":"犯咗國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a3c78791aa93d1750ca306e58bb6026f947fee","tid":2489710,"uid":270657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3f8c4d4d3995230b69cbc80f68add536d94d0b6","tid":2489710,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:13:20.000Z","msg":"北京閹割香港選舉制度，民間呈現出「心死」狀態。有民調顯示，對比人大常委會上月底通過「完善」選制前，市民對特首林鄭月娥的評分下跌2.1分，至30.7分水平，而支持林鄭的比率則略為上升。<br />\n<br />\n市民對林鄭反對率微跌1個百分點至67%<br />\n香港民意研究計劃於本月7至9日成功訪問了逾千名市民。結果顯示，市民對林鄭的評分，由上月下旬的32.8分跌至30.7分，而支持率更則微升兩個百分點至20%、反對率微跌1個百分點至67%，使支持率淨值增加3個百分點至負47%。惟細分之下，給予林鄭0分的市民多達41%。<br />\n<br />\n3名司長方面，市民對政務司司長張建宗和律政司司長鄭若驊的評分都有所下調，分別下跌0.1分及1.2分至32.6分及22.7分。至於市民對財政司司長陳茂波的評分，則稍稍增加了1.1分，達35.8分水平。換言之，無論林鄭或3名司長的民望均處於不及格水平。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i83iCbwILR5cAdA6ydmo7FjklgY=/802x891/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WRNL2E3JLVGKLJIBOUGQU7EN34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi83iCbwILR5cAdA6ydmo7FjklgY%3D%2F802x891%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWRNL2E3JLVGKLJIBOUGQU7EN34.jpg&h=8ea93435&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:23:04.000Z","msg":"鄭月娥：從政者不要介意未能取得民望 否則很痛苦"},{"pid":"4ddf1de3b63a0524b4da01b982918039560ae84f","tid":2489710,"uid":24788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:24:37.000Z","msg":"4成0分好似未跌穿過"},{"pid":"9b60d06be31287d4122d45ad0e336b374f178623","tid":2489710,"uid":76804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:24:56.000Z","msg":"佢應該愈低分愈興奮"},{"pid":"4107530fc638de28380a5c6c03c7482d4a80cf79","tid":2489710,"uid":63939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:26:05.000Z","msg":"林鄭邏輯：重有6成支持我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c93a02b32c10d22755626b4c2663c9323df070","tid":2489710,"uid":39492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"777: 閱，哦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4b1792ed17059a861dd68aaf72e2fb0f2f4fb2","tid":2489710,"uid":396978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8a83604c1734887e515ba08aa209b8dc594990","tid":2489710,"uid":305358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20